right click MCP and open the button -- CTRL + V the following into your innerspace Console. ( most people use the ` key )

Obj_OgreMCP:PasteButton[RawCommand,PrePull,oc,!c,-AbilityTag,AUTO,PreCastTag,13,Allow,AUTO]

for IRC OPTION use

Obj_OgreMCP:PasteButton[RawCommand,PrePull,irc,!c,-AbilityTag,AUTO,PreCast,13,Allow,AUTO]
